article_title: Why A Walgreens Bid For WebMD Makes Some Sense

article_metadata.description: Even though digital health information company WebMD (WBMD) now says it's not "in any negotiations to be acquired," a potential suitor like Walgreens Boots Alliance or UnitedHealth Group would still make some sense if either has the desire to spend the money. The news of potential bidders comes as large healthcare corporations like Walgreens [...]
